atch this: <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/lKudtaIkZs\">https:\/\/t.co\/lKudtaIkZs<\/a><\/p>\n<p>Learn more: <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/NpdHzGsShX\">https:\/\/t.co\/NpdHzGsShX<\/a> <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/t.co\/rH0FjGdYtX\">pic.twitter.com\/rH0FjGdYtX<\/a><\/p>\n<p>\u2014 Nifty Gateway (@niftygateway) <a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/niftygateway\/status\/1509169191022116870?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">March 30, 2022<\/a><\/p>\n<\/blockquote>\n<p>According to the press release, Samsung has already integrated its latest displays with the Nifty Gateway ecosystem. Owners of Samsung\u2019s QLED and Neo QLED smart televisions can now <strong>browse thousands of NFTs<\/strong>, in addition to trading and purchasing any that catch their eye. All this from the safety of the couch-dwelling TV connoisseur\u2019s trusty steed.<\/p>\n<p>\u201c<em>Nifty Gateway\u2019s mission is to bring NFTs to a billion people by empowering creators and simplifying the way customers buy, sell, create, and hold NFTs. We are committed to making NFTs accessible and NFT purchasing more seamless than ever before<\/em>,\u201d \u2013 Duncan Cock Foster \u2013 Nifty Gateway.<\/p>\n<p><b>Want more? Connect with NFT Plazas<\/b><\/p>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/mailchi.mp\/ecadf05eb1bf\/1\">Join the Weekly Newsletter<br \/><\/a><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/discord.gg\/qSQwMaM\">Join our Discord<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/twitter.com\/nftplazas\">Follow us on Twitter<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.facebook.com\/nftplazas\">Like us on Facebook<\/a><br \/><a rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/nftplazas\/\">Follow us on Instagram<\/a><\/p>\